                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Jeandesign/">DizzyWhale</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2010-02-07</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">因为我们相信，所以才真实；并非真实，我们才相信。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="519502468">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-519502468" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-519502468" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="519502468">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/actor9527/">Jim Moriarty</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2013-06-18</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">谣言是群体犯罪的结果，但谣言并不一定是罪行。分析谣言的深层含义远比追查谣言源头更有趣，谣言是填补大众传媒的重要信息通道，没有谣言的社会是可怕的</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="303863352">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-303863352" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-303863352" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="303863352">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/cucub/">大魔卐</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2011-11-07</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">342/18,27-30,61-77,82-100,破解谣言，制造谣言116,128-133,138,146-148,158,-166,213-217,245-260,265,277，301，几本书配合起来，可以搞个主题阅读</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="518490488">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-518490488" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-518490488" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="518490488">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/nwwfewx/">伊卡洛斯</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2012-04-09</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">公众有爱好不幸、灾祸、死亡的病态倾向。谣言远不是有幻觉的人一时神经错乱的行为，而是一个警告的呼声，是我们根深蒂固的感情获得安慰。所以，闲言碎语，无需真实。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

